response.overview: Featuring the Traktor-directed videos for the hit singles "Baby's Got a Temper" and "A Day at Work," this collection provides a fitting demonstration of the energy and showmanship of British electronica superstars the Prodigy. In addition to the music videos, this program also features a compilation of behind-the-scenes footage and a brief "making of" documentary.
response.title: Prodigy: Baby's Got a Temper
